From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: user <user@localhost>
Date: Fri, 14 Mar 2026 15:00:00 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 1/2] device: Battery optimization properties

- Fix render_ahead=20 -> 2 (GPU was rendering 20 frames ahead)
- Remove display skip_validate disable (saves 60 validate calls/sec)
- Remove CoreSight STM tracing (debug infrastructure)
- Disable kernel log forwarding to logd
- Disable STB debug logging
- Disable Qualcomm system daemon (diagnostics)
- Disable WFD debug logging
- Lower big cluster min freq 1.1GHz -> 633MHz (match little cluster)

